title: NRDC Ratings, Popular Swimming Beaches, United States 2009
name: NRDC Ratings, Popular Swimming Beaches, United States 2009
description: This is a csv of NRDC Ratings for a Sample of 200 Popular Swimming Beaches in the United States. Beaches were geocoded for latitude and longitude and spot checked. Contains data on water quality health standards, frequency of testing, failure percentages, and whether or not the beach issues postings and closings advisories
